{"type":"message","id":"fed58727","parentId":"68a6361a","timestamp":"2026-03-19T20:09:25.454Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Fri 2026-03-20 04:09 GMT+8] [Subagent Context] You are running as a subagent (depth 1/1). Results auto-announce to your requester; do not busy-poll for status.\n\n[Subagent Task]: 请帮我搜索以下四个领域的最新行业动态（2026年3月）：\n1. 企业数字化转型\n2. 智能安防\n3. 网络系统集成\n4. IT运维服务\n\n每个领域搜索1-2条关键信息，整理成简洁的笔记格式。我需要落地到中国企业数字化/智能化相关的内容。"}],"timestamp":1773950965451}}
{"type":"message","id":"f06eb861","parentId":"fed58727","timestamp":"2026-03-19T20:09:30.181Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户要求我搜索四个领域的最新行业动态（2026年3月），每个领域1-2条关键信息，整理成简洁的笔记格式。我需要落地到中国企业数字化/智能化相关的内容。\n\n我应该使用web-search skill来进行搜索。让我先读取这个skill的说明。","thinkingSignature":"b89c23c90a28a523e1bdb4ea8553ec75adc62b18df50d5586874432575774715"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_3k0qrsznndrk_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"~/workspace/agent/skills/miaoda-web-search/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":117,"output":99,"cacheRead":18914,"cacheWrite":11827,"totalTokens":30957,"cost":{"input":0.0000351,"output":0.0001188,"cacheRead":0.0005674199999999999,"cacheWrite":0.0014192399999999998,"total":0.0021405599999999997}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773950965453}}
{"type":"message","id":"d4ab82d1","parentId":"f06eb861","timestamp":"2026-03-19T20:09:30.196Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_3k0qrsznndrk_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\r\nname: miaoda-web-search\r\ndescription: \"ALWAYS use this skill FIRST when you need to find, look up, or verify ANY information from the internet — do NOT guess URLs and fetch them directly. Provides necessary command usage instructions for keyword-based web search with AI-generated summaries. 触发词：搜索, 网页搜索, 搜一下, 查一下, 查询, 了解, 找一下, 帮我看看, web search, look up, find out, search, 搜索摘要, 查资料, 搜索引擎, 最新信息, 最近动态\"\r\noverride-tools:\r\n  - web_search\r\n---\r\n\r\n# Web Search\r\n\r\n通过 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary` 按关键词搜索互联网信息，由 AI 自动总结。\r\n\r\n## Quick Reference\r\n\r\n| 参数 | 说明 | 必需 | 默认值 |\r\n|------|------|------|--------|\r\n| `--query` | 搜索关键词（1-500 字符） | 是 | - |\r\n| `--output, -o` | 输出格式: text/json | 否 | text |\r\n\r\n## 命令选择决策树\r\n\r\n```\r\n用户想获取互联网信息\r\n├─ 有具体 URL → miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill）\r\n├─ 无具体 URL，需搜索 → miaoda-studio-cli search-summary\r\n└─ 先搜索再深入 → search-summary 获取 URL → web-crawl 提取详情（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill）\r\n```\r\n\r\n## 使用示例\r\n\r\n```bash\r\n# 按关键词搜索\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"React 19 新特性\"\r\n\r\n# 搜索并获取 JSON 输出\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"ByteDance 开源项目\" --output json\r\n```\r\n\r\n## Common Mistakes\r\n\r\n| 错误 | 正确做法 |\r\n|------|----------|\r\n| 无具体 URL 时用 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl` | 无 URL 用 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary`，有 URL 用 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl`（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill） |\r\n| 搜索关键词超过 500 字符 | 提炼核心关键词，保持精简 |\r\n| 需要后续程序处理结果但未加 `--output json` | 需要解析结果时始终加 `--output json` |\r\n| 命令失败后不检查退出码 | 退出码 `1` 表示失败，检查参数和网络后重试 |\r\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773950970193}}
{"type":"message","id":"8ef58b3a","parentId":"d4ab82d1","timestamp":"2026-03-19T20:09:47.531Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，我需要使用 miaoda-studio-cli search-summary 来搜索这四个领域的最新行业动态。我会为每个领域分别搜索2026年3月的最新信息。\n\n让我搜索四个领域：\n1. 企业数字化转型 2026年3月 中国\n2. 智能安防 2026年3月 中国\n3. 网络系统集成 2026年3月 中国\n4. IT运维服务 2026年3月 中国\n\n我会分别执行搜索命令。","thinkingSignature":"3dfeb336b1f61dd42862f49cd63890c86a2f695c8b907e7f2740e3caa6ca13af"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_7ul4c1m5e5nm_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"企业数字化转型 2026年3月 中国 行业动态\"","timeout":60}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_7ul4c1m5e5nm_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"智能安防 2026年3月 中国 行业动态\"","timeout":60}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_7ul4c1m5e5nm_3","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"网络系统集成 2026年3月 中国 行业动态\"","timeout":60}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_7ul4c1m5e5nm_4","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"IT运维服务 2026年3月 中国 行业动态\"","timeout":60}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":860,"output":307,"cacheRead":30612,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":31779,"cost":{"input":0.000258,"output":0.0003684,"cacheRead":0.0009183599999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00154476}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773950970196}}
